The paper discusses the concept of collaboratories, which is a key area of research in computer-supported cooperative work (CSCW). Therefore, cs.CSCW is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of technology in collaboratories, which is relevant to the sub-categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and social informatics (cs.SI). The paper also mentions the use of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in collaboratories.
